# Sample TB corpus: commit only the US-Government public-domain docs (FDA drug
# labels + CDC curriculum) and provenance. NWT Crown-copyright files are marked
# "not for redistribution" in SOURCES.md, so they stay local (grab them via the
# URLs there).
!data/kb/tb/
data/kb/tb/*
!data/kb/tb/SOURCES.md
!data/kb/tb/fda-*.pdf
!data/kb/tb/cdc-core-curriculum-tb.pdf
.pytest_cache/
*.egg-info/
web/node_modules/
web/dist/
web/.env

